@startuml
skinparam actor {
  BorderColor DarkBlue
  BackgroundColor LightBlue
  FontSize 14
}
skinparam usecase {
  BorderColor Green
  BackgroundColor LightGreen
  FontSize 14
}
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam noteBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam noteBorderColor DarkRed

title US28: View Population of a Specific Region

actor "Data Analyst" as DA
rectangle "Population Reporting System" as SystemBoundary {
  usecase "View Population of a Specific Region" as UCR
}

DA --> UCR : Requests report

note left of UCR: Key Extensions:\n- Invalid region name: Handle error and retry\n- Database query failure: Notify user\n- No population data available: Inform and end

@enduml